snippet.title: MAN WAXING and DEPILATION torture  �� It might HURT, but still FUNNY tho!
snippet.description:
We all know, it is kinda painful, and men are not used to it. But sometimes, before summer, it is a-must! No pain, no gain! :D These poor guys had to go through some tough moments so that we can watch them laughing at them :D However, big respect to 'em ;) 
So super funny! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
